    ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

    Warning klaxons echo through the reactor control room. The massive
    fusion reactor at the heart of the Odyssey hums with barely contained
    power. Multiple configuration files have been corrupted, and manual
    intervention is required.

    Chief Engineer Tanaka's repair scripts are still in the system, but
    they need to be modified and executed to restore full functionality.

    ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
    │  REACTOR STATUS                                                    │
    │  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────  │
    │                                                                     │
    │  ⚠ Configuration files: CORRUPTED (needs patching)                 │
    │  ⚠ Batch operations: REQUIRED (multiple files affected)            │
    │  ⚠ Repair scripts: NEED MODIFICATION                               │
    │                                                                     │
    │  To restore the reactor, you'll need to use text manipulation      │
    │  tools and write shell scripts to automate the repairs.            │
    │                                                                     │
    └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

    ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

    SECTOR 3 SKILLS:
    • sed          - Stream editor for text manipulation
    • xargs        - Build commands from input
    • Shell scripts - Automate repair procedures
    • chmod        - Manage file permissions

    Begin your mission: cat .mission

